npm -> node package manager tha namm but abhi ye hata diya gya hi ise khali npm bolteb hai kyunnki ispe ab node ke alawa aur bhi cchizo ke package milte hai

ALL THE NPM PACKAGES ARE PRESENT ON THIS WEBSITE -> https://www.npmjs.com/ <-

Package vs Modules -> Jo node js ke sath preinstalled aata hai use Modules bolte aur jinhe ham npm se download karte hai unhe Package bolte hai

installing and uninstalling packages in npm ->
installing :-> npm i [package name]
uninstalling :-> npm uninstall [package name]

installing specific version of a package -> npm i [PackageName]@version

<------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------>
dependencies -> packages aur un packages ki depencies(Yani wo kisi aur package pe depend to nhi hai)
devdependencies -> Aise packages jo ki khali development ke time pe time use hote aur deployment ke baad unka koe nam nhi hota unhe devdependencies kahte hai --:>( npm i [PackageName] --save-dev )
<------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------>

scripts in npm ->
for running any script on npm we have to run command( npm run [script.js] )
but > stop < < & > > test <  are the two scripts that can be used without using run command ( npm test/stop ) but that node modules me jake package.json file me us script ko add karna padega like start and test one.